# Implementation Plan - Add Pujari Registration Button

This plan outlines the steps to add a "Pujari Registration" button to the application, ensuring it directs users to the registration form with the "Pujari" role pre-selected.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The "Pujari Registration" button will be added to both the Header (Navigation Bar) and the Hero Section of the home page to ensure maximum visibility for service providers.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Internationalization (i18n)
Add the translation keys for the new button.

#### [MODIFY] [en.json](file:///e:/praveen/ayyaruapp_v1/src/i18n/locales/en.json)
- Add `"Register_Pujari": "Pujari Registration"`
- Add `"hero_pujari_cta": "Register as Pujari"`

#### [MODIFY] [te.json](file:///e:/praveen/ayyaruapp_v1/src/i18n/locales/te.json)
- Add `"Register_Pujari": "పూజారి రిజిస్ట్రేషన్"`
- Add `"hero_pujari_cta": "పూజారిగా నమోదు చేసుకోండి"`

### 2. Login Page Logic
Enhance the login page to handle query parameters for user convenience.

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///e:/praveen/ayyaruapp_v1/app/login/page.tsx)
- Use `useSearchParams` to detect `mode=signup` and `role=Pujari`.
- Initialize `isLogin` and `role` states based on these parameters.

### 3. Components
Add the button to the UI.

#### [MODIFY] [Header.tsx](file:///e:/praveen/ayyaruapp_v1/src/components/Header.tsx)
- Add a "Pujari Registration" link next to the Login button in desktop view.
- Add it to the mobile menu as well.
- Style it to be distinct from the regular login button (e.g., secondary style or outline).

#### [MODIFY] [HeroSection.tsx](file:///e:/praveen/ayyaruapp_v1/src/components/HeroSection.tsx)
- Add a second CTA button below the main "Start Now" button specifically for Pujaris.

## Open Questions

- Should the button style match the "Login" button exactly, or should it be a secondary/outline button to distinguish it?
- Is there any specific landing page for Pujaris, or should it go directly to the signup form? (Assuming signup form for now based on current app structure).

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- None planned as this is mostly UI/UX.

### Manual Verification
1. Click the "Pujari Registration" button in the Header.
2. Verify it redirects to `/login?mode=signup&role=Pujari`.
3. Verify the signup form is open and "Pujari" is selected in the role dropdown.
4. Check the mobile menu for the same button.
5. Check the Hero Section for the new CTA.
6. Toggle languages and verify translations.
